es.uam.eps.ir.ranksys.fast.preference

Interface FastPreferenceData<U,I,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    U - type of the users
    I - type of the items
    V - type of other information about preferences
    All Superinterfaces:
    FastItemIndex<I>, FastUserIndex<U>, ItemIndex<I>, PreferenceData<U,I,V>, UserIndex<U>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFastPreferenceData, SimpleFastPreferenceData, TransposedPreferenceData

    public interface FastPreferenceData<U,I,V>
extends PreferenceData<U,I,V>, FastUserIndex<U>, FastItemIndex<I>
    Fast version of PreferenceData, where preferences for users and items are stored internally by the indexes provided by FastUserIndex and FastItemIndex.
    Author:
    Sa√∫l Vargas (saul.vargas@uam.es)
